{"article_id":"MSoBWa23aqyh78EI","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"After sending signals this week","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"that compromise was possible ,","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"both Barack Obama and John Boehner on Saturday reiterated their opposing positions on Saturday ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"with the president insisting on higher taxes on the wealthy","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"and the Republican House speaker calling for tax code reform and overall lower tax rates .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"President Obama ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"who has invited Mr. Boehner and other congressional leaders to join him in the White House next week","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"to begin looking for a way","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"to avoid the \" fiscal cliff , \" the series of automatic spending cuts and tax hikes","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"set to kick in at the end of the year ,","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"said","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"part of that solution will require higher taxes for those","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"making more than $ 250,000 .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"\" If we ' re serious about reducing the deficit ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"we have to combine spending cuts with revenue","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"- and that means asking the wealthiest Americans to pay a little more in taxes , \"","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"the president said in his weekly Internet and radio address .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"\" That ' s how we did it","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"when Bill Clinton was president .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"And that ' s the only way","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"we can afford to invest in education and job training and manufacturing - all the ingredients of a strong middle class and a strong economy . \"","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"The president repeated his contention from a day earlier","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"that the results of Tuesday ' s election ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"in which the nation ' s voters returned the Democratic incumbent to the White House","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"and added more Democrats to the Senate and the House ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"constituted a mandate for \" action . \"","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"\" On Tuesday , America went to the polls .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"And the message","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"you sent","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"was clear :","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"You voted for action , not politics as usual .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"You elected us to focus on your jobs , not ours , \"","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"\" That ' s why I ' ve invited leaders of both parties to the White House next week ,","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"so we can start to build consensus around challenges","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"we can only solve together . \"","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"\" This is even more important","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"because at the end of this year , we face a series of deadlines","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"that require us to make major decisions","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"about how to pay down our deficit","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"-","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"decisions","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"that will have a huge impact on the economy and the middle class , now and in the future , \"","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"Part of the \" fiscal cliff \"","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"facing the U.S. economy","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"involves the scheduled expiration of the Bush tax cuts ,","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"which would result in an across-the-boards tax hike in 2013 .","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"The president urged Republicans to take action","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"to avoid that scenario .","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"\" We need a majority in Congress","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"to listen","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"- and they should start","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"by making sure","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"taxes don ' t go up on the 98 percent of Americans","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"making under $ 250,000 a year","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"starting January 1 .","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"This is something","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"we all agree on , \"","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"the president said .","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"Mr. Boehner has said","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"tax increases will send the fragile American economy back into a double-dip recession .","depth":5},{"id":62,"text":"\" Instead of raising tax rates on the American people","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"and accepting the damage","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"it will do to our economy ,","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"let ' s start to actually solve the problem .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"Let ' s focus on tax reform","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"that closes special interest loopholes","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"and lowers tax rates , \"","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"the Ohio Republican said in the GOP ' s weekly address .","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"\" If there was a mandate in this election ,","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"it was a mandate","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"to work together","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"to do what ' s in the best interest of our country , \"","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"the Republican leader said .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"\" And right now , what ' s best is getting our economy moving again","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"and keeping it moving ,","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"so we can begin to restore our children ' s future . \"","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"Mr. Boehner and Republicans support extending the Bush tax cuts .","depth":2},{"id":79,"text":"The White House supports the extension on income under $ 250,000 ,","depth":3},{"id":80,"text":"but wants to see higher rates rise on income above that level .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":161,"left":158,"right":160,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"